{
  "stem": "11174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now they wanted-- they thought also maybe is going to be a normal life, brought it up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were carrying it to help them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We slept there one night, I think, or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the-- the men came back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were still with them together until, all of a sudden-- wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Yom Kippur there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The interesting thing was that one day, we were short on cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the girls there-- there were two single girls there-- [INAUDIBLE]-- went out to the German soldiers and asked them for-- for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, when it was quiet, when they didn't-- And everything was quiet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, this was supposed to be-- all of a sudden they said all the Jews have to leave town, because the San, that river, was supposed to be the border between Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't care where you go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we all started to go to this little-- to the next town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Ulanow, back to where I was Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the day after Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went with this family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, this family had a few wagons in the front of the house to take all the goods, the piece goods along, you know, to have a little-- little stack for-- for livelihood, for living.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans were standing there, officers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a lot of Polish people, mostly fellows and girls, laughing, having fun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the German officers, were [INAUDIBLE]-- if a nice piece came in, took it away, give it her, give it to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were having a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
